<h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="feature-codes"><code>FeatureCodes</code> and <code>FeatureAccessMode</code></h3>
<p class="govuk-body">
    Features are global product areas. Each <code>Feature</code> row holds
    an <code>AccessMode</code> (<code>Off / OnForAll / OnForSome</code>) plus
    join tables (<code>FeatureUserAllow</code>, <code>FeatureGroupAllow</code>)
    that scope <code>OnForSome</code> to specific people. Codes consumed by
    feature-gate filters and nav flags:
</p>

