<h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="permission-type"><code>PermissionType</code></h3>
<p class="govuk-body">
    <code>PermissionType</code> (<code>Models/GroupFeaturePermission.cs:34-40</code>):
    <code>View = 1</code>, <code>Create = 2</code>, <code>Update = 3</code>,
    <code>Delete = 4</code>. Stored as columns on <code>GroupFeaturePermission</code>
    (one row per <code>(GroupId, FeatureId, PermissionType)</code>).
</p>

