<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="attributes">Authorization attributes</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    All custom authorization attributes live in <code>Attributes/</code> and
    implement <code>IAsyncAuthorizationFilter</code> (or
    <code>IAsyncActionFilter</code> for the API and feature-permission ones).
    They are applicable at class or method level. Every check delegates to
    <code>IPermissionService</code>, resolved per-request via
    <code>HttpContext.RequestServices.GetRequiredService&lt;IPermissionService&gt;()</code>.
</p>

<div class="developers-data-models">
    <table class="govuk-table">
        <caption class="govuk-table__caption govuk-visually-hidden">Compass authorization attributes</caption>
        <thead class="govuk-table__head">
